text: Irina Bara and Valentina Ivakhnenko were the defending champions, but both players chose not to participate. Manon Arcangioli and Kimberley Zimmermann won the title, defeating Victoria Rodríguez and Ioana Loredana Roșca in the final, 2–6, 6–3, [10–6]. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ===Draw=== ==References== *Main Draw Engie Open de Biarritz - Doubles
